---
layout: layouts/minimal.njk
title: Characters
---

<div class="relative p-3 mb-3 bg-white rounded-md shadow-lg overflow-hidden w-full prose prose-headings:my-3 max-w-none">
  <h1>Characters</h1>
  <p>Known usually from my profile pictures across platforms, I do have a few original characters that I designed over the years. Here you can find their profiles and references!</p>
  <p class="font-bold">Individual profiles are coming soon!</p>
</div>
<div class="grid gap-3 grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2">
  {% for character in characters %}
    <a class="
        relative 
        flex items-end 
        bg-white bg-[url('{{ character.cover }}')] bg-center bg-cover bg-no-repeat 
        rounded-md shadow-lg overflow-hidden 
        h-[200px] md:h-[100px]
        transition-all
        {% if not character.enabled %}grayscale hover:grayscale-[0.5] cursor-not-allowed{% endif %}" 
        {% if character.enabled %}href="/characters/{{character.nickname}}/"{% else %}href="#"{% endif %}>
      <div class="w-full px-3 py-1 bg-white/75 uppercase italic font-bold">{{ character.nickname }}</div>
    </a>
  {% endfor %}
</div>